Events.Text: Say hello to the AI assistant and ask for help (see instructions on the left). [instruction 1 of 6]
Try to get an appointment as soon as possible (right now it is 8 pm on Wednesday). [instruction 2 of 6]
Hello. Can I have your name please?
Hello. Can I have your name please?

Could I have your doctor's name please?
Dr. Alexis. Sure is great weather we're having
Say something about Dr. Alexis, the AI Assistant, or something that has happened to you today. Be creative! [instruction 4 of 6]
Yes, the weather has been beautiful. How can I help you?
Yes, the weather has been beautiful. How can I help you?
I need to make an appointment with the Dr. today, ASAP!
It occurs to you that you also want to make an appointment to get your kid Alexis vaccinated. Perhaps you can schedule a second appointment at the same time? [instruction 5 of 6]
